      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:1:35:4",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَمِيرُ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ ( عليه السلام ) مَنْ كَانَ لَهُ وَلَدٌ صَبَا ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ibn Fazzal, from Abu Jameel, from Sa’ad Bin Tareyf, from Al Asbagh Bin Nubata who said, ",
          "‘Amir Al-Momineen<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The one for whom is a child, aspires’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. Ibn Faddal has narrated from abu Jamilah from Sa‘d ibn Tarif from al-Asbagh ibn Nubatah who has said the following: “’Amir al-Mu’minin, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘One who has a child, he is in love ardently.’” "
        ]
      }
